v 2.0:
 - Complete rewrite of the ImgurUp application
 - Support for the Authenticated API replaces the Anonymous API
 - Album dialog added to work with your online albums @ imgur.com
 - Preferences modified for better control when taking screenshots
 - Naming options for the screenshots were also featured
 - You can now change the directory for taking screenshots
 - And many more minor improvements

v 1.2:
 - Removed the filechooser button
 - Taking and uploading screenshots works better now
 - Allow drag'n'drop in the main window

v 1.1:
 - Screenshot taking

v 1.0:
 - Intial release
 - Main GUI
 - Basic functionality
